'''Alexandr Kliment''' (January 30, 1929 – March 22, 2017) was a [[Czech Republic|Czech]] writer, poet and [[playwright]]. He was a signatory of [[Charter 77]] in 1977.<ref name=idnes>{{cite news |first=|last=|title=Zemřel spisovatel a publicista Alexandr Kliment, signatář Charty 77 |url=http://zpravy.idnes.cz/zemrel-alexandr-kliment-signatar-charta-77-fg4-/domaci.aspx?c=A170322_201202_domaci_pku |work=[[Mladá fronta DNES]] |publisher= |date=2017-03-22 |accessdate=2017-04-18}}</ref>
In 1967, Kliment participated in a congress of the writers' union, which included [[Václav Havel]], [[Ivan Klíma]], [[Ludvík Vaculík]], and photographer [[Oldřich Škácha]].<ref name=rp>{{cite news |first=Ian|last=Willoughby|title=Oldřich Škácha – photographer of Havel and others |url=http://www.radio.cz/en/section/panorama/oldrich-skacha-photographer-of-havel-and-others |work=[[Radio Prague]] |publisher= |date=2010-12-08 |accessdate=2017-04-17}}</ref> The writers' congress, which took place during a period of liberalism in [[Czechoslovakia]], is considered to be a predecessor of the [[Prague Spring]] in 1968.<ref name=rp/> He later joined with Havel and other Czechoslovak dissidents to sign the Charter 77.<ref name=idnes/>
Kliment died on March 21, 2017, at the age of 88.<ref name=idnes/><ref name=nov>{{cite news |first=|last=|title=Zemřel spisovatel a publicista Alexandr Kliment, signatář Charty |url=https://www.novinky.cz/kultura/432889-zemrel-spisovatel-a-publicista-alexandr-kliment-signatar-charty.html |work=[[Novinky.cz]] |publisher= |date=2017-03-22 |accessdate=2017-04-18}}</ref>
