'''Jason A. Fox''' (born 29 December 1983) is a [[Melbourne]] based [[thought leader]], author and motivational speaker.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.workplaceleadership.com.au/events/clever-happenings/|title=Clever Happenings – Centre for Workplace Leadership|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://fedsquare.com/events/99u-local-melbourne|title=99U Local: Melbourne – Federation Square|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{cite web|url=http://www.drjasonfox.com/read/fol2014|title=The Future of Leadership|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref name=":2">{{cite web|url=http://www.drjasonfox.com/read/fol2015?rq=Future%20of%20Leadership|title=The Future of Leadership: Workplace Culture|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{cite web|url=http://www.smh.com.au/nsw/male-speakers-boycott-allmale-panels-to-protest-lack-of-female-representation-20160428-gohb4k.html|title=Male speakers boycott all-male panels to protest lack of female representation|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref>
==Career== Fox's career as a speaker spans [[fortune 500]].<ref name="drjasonfox.com">{{cite web|url=http://www.drjasonfox.com/about/|title=About|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref name=":4">{{Cite web|url=http://professionalspeakers.org.au/about/awards/|title=The Nevin Award, Keynote Presenter & Educator Award for Excellence|website=''professionalspeakers.org.au''|access-date=24 June 2016}}</ref> As a speaker, he has been a part of numerous self organised events<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":1" /><ref name=":2" /> as well as of those organised by others<ref name=":3" /><ref>{{cite web|url=https://creativemornings.com/talks/dr-jason-fox|title=Dr Jason Fox – CreativeMornings/Stockholm|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>http://www.gartner.com/imagesrv/summits/docs/apac/business-intelligence/BIIM_2014_Trip_Report.pdf</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ahri.com.au/stateconferences/location/melbourne/speakers|title=Speakers – Australian Human Resources Institute|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.behance.net/gallery/20776439/Dr-Jason-Fox-on-Motivation-Strategy-Design|title=Behance|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://purpose.do/speakers/dr-jason/|title=Dr Jason Fox|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref> and has also been cited among one of the male speakers who have boycotted all male speaker panels as a way to protest against lack of female representation.<ref name=":3" />
Fox was awarded ''Keynote Speaker of the Year'' award for 2016 by Professional Speakers Australia.<ref name="drjasonfox.com" /><ref name=":4" />
Jason A. Fox is the best-selling author of ''The Game Changer''.<ref name="auto"/> His recent work, ''How to Lead a Quest'', also became a best selling book.<ref name="auto1"/> Fox's research has been cited by Smart Company,<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.smartcompany.com.au/people-human-resources/41380-why-business-owners-should-think-like-game-designers/|title=Why business owners should think like game designers – SmartCompany|last=Administrator|date=3 April 2014|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref> [[BRW (magazine)|BRW]] and [[The Financial Review]]<ref name="drjasonfox.com"/> among others.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.cmo.com.au/blog/leading-way/2014/03/14/level-your-productivity-thinking-game-designer/|title=Level-up your productivity by thinking like a game designer|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.drjasonfox.com/read/|title=Read|accessdate=21 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://switchedonleadership.com/issue-29-switched-leadership-featuring-dr-jason-fox/|title=Issue 29: Switched on Leadership Featuring Dr Jason Fox • Switched on Leadership|date=12 April 2016|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://collectivehub.com/2016/04/video-the-damaging-power-of-self-sabotage/|title=VIDEO: The Damaging Power of Self-Sabotage|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.hrmonline.com.au/section/opinion/book-review-how-to-lead-a-quest-by-dr-jason-fox/|title=Book Review: How to Lead a Quest, by Dr Jason Fox – HRM online|date=18 April 2016|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.clarkmorgan.com/when-managing-change-focus-on-progress-not-goals-jason-fox/|title=When Managing Change, Focus on Progress, Not Goals – Jason Fox – ClarkMorgan Ltd. – Evolving People|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mynewsdesk.com/fi/fibs/news/in-search-of-meaningful-progress-with-dr-jason-fox-169176|title=In search of meaningful progress with Dr Jason Fox|accessdate=24 June 2016}}</re