'''Sa Bangji'''(사방지,舍方知) was a Korean [[intersex]] person during the [[Joseon Dynasty]]. Sa Bangji had [[hypospadias]] and was [[gender of rearing|reared as]] a girl. Sa Bangji had [[sexual relationship]]s with widows and [[Bhikkhuni]]s.<ref>[http://www.sciencetimes.co.kr/?news=%EB%B0%98%EC%9D%8C%EC%96%91-%EC%9D%B8%EA%B0%84-%EC%82%AC%EB%B0%A9%EC%A7%80%EC%9D%98-%EB%B9%84%EB%B0%80-%EB%B0%9D%ED%98%80%EC%A7%88%EA%B9%8C 반음양 인간 ‘사방지’의 비밀 밝혀질까]</ref>

